{"tid":1968090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"取名「武漢肺炎」…竟遭遊戲公司威脅：再取就永久封鎖","createTime":"2020-04-11T11:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T13:33:00.000Z","uid":266508,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9a43202343229cee61ec0fdcc6edfaa4c18e45","tid":1968090,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）的稱呼一直是中國民眾相當在意的焦點，因其認為「武漢肺炎」一詞是在汙名化中國，不許任何人事物提起。在先前台灣玩家因取名「武漢肺炎」被全地圖中國玩家討伐後，仍有玩家不信邪，在別款遊戲實測武漢肺炎的殺傷力，不料遭到了來自「遊戲官方」的追殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Njs7tv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Njs7tv.jpg&h=d55a200e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友於Dcard上發文，表示近期因為不少遊戲取名「武漢肺炎」都會遭到警告，決定在自己遊玩多年的手遊《部落衝突：皇室戰爭》上測試。其特意改名為「武漢ㄈㄟˋ一ㄢˊ中國ㄅㄧㄥㄉㄨ」，以避免官方的查緝，結果還是被官方注意到了，其帳號遭到封禁2天，原因是「您的帳號名字令人不適」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuXLfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuXLfS.jpg&h=9d847156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在解除2天的封鎖後，遊戲ID遭官方強制更改為「皇室菁英」。該玩家仍不死心，再度付費改名為「武漢ㄈㄟˋ一ㄢˊ中國ㄅㄧㄥㄉㄨ」。不久後便被官方再度封禁，封禁時間也從2天延長至7天，且下達了最後通牒「如果再次違反我們的遊戲規則或服務條款，我們將&middot;永&middot;久&middot;封&middot;禁&middot;此帳號，望您知曉」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，芬蘭遊戲開發商SUPERCELL所製作的《部落衝突：皇室戰爭》為何會對武漢肺炎如此敏感呢？因其早在2016年6月便被中國遊戲產業龍頭《騰訊》收購，以86億美元收購了84.3%的股份，達成控股。也就是如此&hellip;該名玩家才會一再受到遊戲公司的封禁甚至是警告，可見其對於武漢肺炎的敏感程度。<br />\n<br />\n三立新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=723709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D723709&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ac47dbbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D723709&h=dc2c2ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=723709</a>"},{"pid":"65e08f35ab0c55fb770b49c9921d804da610ae4d","tid":1968090,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"{CCTVB戰線] 美國網民玩死電視台嘅成功例子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avicQKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avicQKU</a>"},{"pid":"dc68e43c7f37fd4c92f6cf0bd5150ca948785841","tid":1968090,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"我屌，我成日玩都唔知原來又俾騰訊買撚左，好彩未課金"},{"pid":"a47942b22ee87abb3097ca96a80acd3d461e843e","tid":1968090,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"辣殺驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93750fba73a655552c3a8c1db2e805942d62679","tid":1968090,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"呢檔野唔係一早比騰訊收購左㗎咩？"},{"pid":"d4692ddd7fe2f19a295cc6ff1821728dd8849cd2","tid":1968090,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b93750fba73a655552c3a8c1db2e805942d62679","tid":1968090,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"呢檔野唔係一早比騰訊收購左㗎咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"真係唔知喎，不過我都有改左個撚支那既名，但冇俾官方捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45b336ed768a2570b7d8d89c2813231997d4523","tid":1968090,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"依家基本好多game廠都畀企鵝買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477e9680a4beeaa2d44ac6ea0aa9728e52a52b2f","tid":1968090,"uid":227918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4692ddd7fe2f19a295cc6ff1821728dd8849cd2","tid":1968090,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b93750fba73a655552c3a8c1db2e805942d62679","tid":1968090,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04